name: Tina Jennifer
description: I’m warm, caring woman that wants to be in love again and be loved in return. I want to have the companionship of a man, have the security of knowing that he will be there for me. Big strong hugs, long slow kisses. I am open and honest, won’t pout and say “nothing” when you ask me what is wrong when I am in a quiet mood. I sincerely love men and their “guys” world. I won’t try to change you to suit me.I am a classy, independent, confident woman. I am seeking the same in a man. I like all activities especially the water and outdoor type. I like walks along the beach, in the park, on hikes. I am looking for a friendship leading to a long term relationship.
